{
  "stem": "9489.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we have to keep fire on your trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they still used to fall in-- wolves used to invade our trucks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we come in, deep in the jungle, about two hours' drive, were Cossacks and Uzbeks they brought in from Uzbekistan, Kazakhstan.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they build them homes from snow blocks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the middle was fire from wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So some-- if you lay on this side you're warm, and this side you freeze.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we say every day 10, 20 were freezing to death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the morning you wake him up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we didn't live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just were chauffeurs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We come in-- our trailers were already loaded.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just come in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hook them in, you turn, and you went to the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the city was a lake-- you know, frozen lake?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, when summer comes, the wood goes-- the timber.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we was very danger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In-- in there-- the wheels-- you know, what eight-wheelers-- the wheels were made from timber-- from the timber.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was not in air, and the kind of air blows-- doesn't work there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the worst thing was, in the morning you have to wake up, 4 o'clock, to heated up the engine differential, you know, with-- with oil and-- and what do you call them?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Clothes, you know, and kerosene, and mix it up in pails.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you used to warm up the engines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then you got hard water, after you warm up 13 minutes, you keep in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they give you boiling water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Threw boiling water on the engine, and then the radiator, to start it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And how many of these vehicles were you responsible for?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just got-- each one got one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was too-- too weak to start it, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
